  "title": "Operations Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Operations Coordinator will manage overall operation of individual businesses. He/She will be reporting to Operations/Senior Manager in various aspects of operations including franchise operations and development, product development, outlet promotions, nationwide and local store promotional activities (in conjunction with Group Marketing Department)</p><p>• To assist existing franchise outlets on how to increase their sales and</p><p>their contribution profit margin.</p><p>• To provide service and support to existing outlets</p><p>• Maintain good franchise relationships and plan contracts.</p><p>• Handle customer feedbacks and enquiries</p><p>• Perform any other duties as required and directed by the Company</p><p>• To Provide adequate training to new staffs to enhance performance of the whole organisation.</p><p>• Conducts in-house training to staffs on a monthly basis.</p>",
